  "articleDescription": "<p>此协议描述的是由世纪互联运营的 Microsoft Azure 关于运行时间和连接性方面的承诺。单个 Azure 服务的服务级别协议如下所列。 </p>",
  "mainContent": "<h2>AI</h2><ul>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/cognitive-services/index.html\">认知服务</a></li>\n</ul><h2>安全性</h2><ul>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/key-vault/index.html\">密钥保管库</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/active-directory-b2c/index.html\">Azure Active Directory B2C</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/application-gateway/index.html\">应用程序网关</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/vpn-gateway/index.html\">VPN 网关</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/azure-defender/index.html\">安全中心</a></li>\n</ul><h2>标识</h2><ul>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/multi-factor-authentication/index.html\">多重身份验证</a></li>\n</ul><h2>存储</h2><ul>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/storage/index.html\">存储</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/managed-disks/index.html\">托管磁盘</a></li>\n</ul><h2>分析</h2><ul>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/sql-data-warehouse/index.html\">SQL 数据仓库</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/hdinsight/index.html\">HDInsight</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/stream-analytics/index.html\">流分析</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/power-bi-embedded/index.html\">Power BI Embedded</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/analysis-services/index.html\">Azure 分析服务</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/event-hubs/index.html\">事件中心</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/data-factory/index.html\">数据工厂</a></li>\n</ul><h2>管理工具</h2><ul>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/automation/index.html\">自动化</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/backup/index.html\">备份</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/site-recovery/index.html\">站点恢复</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/scheduler/index.html\">计划程序</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/monitor/index.html\">Azure 监控器</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/traffic-manager/index.html\">流量管理器</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/network-watcher/index.html\">网络观察程序</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/data-explorer/index.html\">Azure 数据资源管理器</a></li>\n</ul><h2>集成</h2><ul>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/service-bus/index.html\">服务总线</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/api-management/index.html\">API 管理</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/event-grid/index.html\">事件网格</a></li>\n</ul><h2>计算</h2><ul>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/virtual-machines/index.html\">虚拟机</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/virtual-machine-scale-sets/index.html\">虚拟机规模集</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/app-service/index.html\">应用服务</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/service-fabric/index.html\">Service Fabric</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/cloud-services/index.html\">云服务</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/functions/index.html\">Functions</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/kubernetes-service/index.html\">Azure Kubernetes 服务（AKS）</a></li>\n</ul><h2>联网</h2><ul>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/dns/index.html\">DNS</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/load-balancer/index.html\">负载均衡器</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/application-gateway/index.html\">应用程序网关</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/vpn-gateway/index.html\">VPN 网关</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/cdn/index.html\">CDN</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/traffic-manager/index.html\">流量管理器</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/expressroute/index.html\">ExpressRoute</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/network-watcher/index.html\">网络观察程序</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/azure-firewall/index.html\">Azure 防火墙</a></li>\n</ul><h2>媒体</h2><ul>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/media-services/index.html\">媒体服务</a></li>\n</ul><h2>迁移</h2><ul>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/site-recovery/index.html\">站点恢复</a></li>\n</ul><h2>容器</h2><ul>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/app-service/index.html\">应用服务</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/service-fabric/index.html\">Service Fabric</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/container-registry/index.html\">容器注册表</a></li>\n</ul><h2>数据库</h2><ul>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/managed-instance/index.html\">SQL 托管实例</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/sql-data/index.html\">SQL 数据库</a></li>\n<!-- <li><a href=\"/support/sla/mysqldatabaseonazure/\">MySQL Database on Azure</a></li> -->\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/sql-data-warehouse/index.html\">SQL 数据仓库</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/sql-server-stretch-database/index.html\">SQL Server 伸展数据库</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/cosmos-db/index.html\">Azure Cosmos DB</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/cache/index.html\">用于 Redis 的 Azure 缓存</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/mysql/index.html\">Azure Database for MySQL</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/postgresql/index.html\">Azure Database for PostgreSQL</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/mariadb/index.html\">Azure Database for MariaDB</a></li>\n</ul><h2>网站</h2><ul>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/app-service/index.html\">应用服务</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/notification-hubs/index.html\">通知中心</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/api-management/index.html\">API 管理</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/cdn/index.html\">CDN</a></li>\n</ul><h2>物联网</h2><ul>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/iot-hub/index.html\">Azure IoT 中心</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/event-hubs/index.html\">事件中心</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/stream-analytics/index.html\">流分析</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/cosmos-db/index.html\">Azure Cosmos DB</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/notification-hubs/index.html\">通知中心</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/api-management/index.html\">API 管理</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/time-series-insights/index.html\">Azure 时序见解</a></li>\n</ul><h2>移动</h2><ul>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/app-service/index.html\">应用服务</a></li>\n</ul><h2>DevOps</h2><ul>\n<li><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/managed-grafana/index.html\">Managed Grafana</a></li>\n</ul><p><a href=\"{base_url}/support/legal/sla/summary/index.html\">所有 Azure 服务的服务级别协议的摘要</a></p><p>点击<a href=\"{base_url}/Images/marketing-resource/media/sla/Consolidated_SLA_Chinese_190905.pdf\">此处</a>可以下载大部分 Azure 服务的服务级别协议</p>"
